                                        <p class="card-text" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; font-size: 30px ; margin-left: -240px; margin-top: 50px; margin-right: 150px; line-height: 116.7%; text-align: center;">Chelsea becomes the place to be seen and the place to watch football played with flair, as manager Tommy Docherty delivers silverware, Dave Sexton adds to the success and star players Peter Osgood, Chopper Harris, Peter Bonetti and many more become household names. A record TV audience is drawn to watch the team in action in an epic encounter against big rivals, and thousands of Blues fans travel to support their heroes abroad against Spanish giants, with some hasty travel replanning required, and it proves not to be in vain!</p>
