                                                            <p class="card-text" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; font-size: 30px ; margin-left: -240px; margin-top: 50px; margin-right: 150px; line-height: 116.7%; text-align: center;">Time is running out for a golden Chelsea generation who have won so much but are missing something big. There has been agony along the way and infamous near misses, but on a May night in Munich there is one more chance. Taking it in the most dramatic of ways proves so sweet that we come back for more. It takes time for a repeat success but a thoroughly deserved one arrives, making Chelsea truly the pride of London...</p>
